<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>Paul Bigby was a graduate of the University of Michigan College of Engineering, class of 1931. Following graduation, Bigby continued to be involved in University alumni activities.</p>
</bioghist>



<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The collection consists almost entirely of topical files, correspondence, and programs relating to his University of Michigan alumni activities, especially the Football Bust and U-M Night.</p>
</scopecontent>

